text: Llewellyn James Owens (26 September 1927 – 1 January 2018) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Fitzroy and South Melbourne in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:2018 deaths Category:1927 births Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Sydney Swans players
